                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="356487" author="yujian" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2022 21:21:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is the back-ported patch for b2_15 branch: &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/49413&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/49413&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="356485" author="yujian" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2022 21:10:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, Peter, there are 13 patches for that ticket. I&apos;m looking at them to see if I can just port #47239.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="356484" author="pjones" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2022 20:52:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ah very good - thanks. So it would probably make sense to port that same patch to b2_15 to reduce test noise?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="356471" author="yujian" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2022 19:23:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The same test was removed from master branch by &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/47239&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/47239&lt;/a&gt; (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10994&quot; title=&quot;remove unused page layers&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10994&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-10994&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; test: remove netdisk from obdfilter-survey&quot;).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="356467" author="yujian" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2022 19:18:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Peter,&lt;br/&gt;
It&apos;s not a regression in 2.15.2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The same failure occurred on:&lt;br/&gt;
2.15.0: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a17b3fbf-ece1-4554-9cb1-02f25578424e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a17b3fbf-ece1-4554-9cb1-02f25578424e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
2.15.1: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ae959a93-3db7-47d4-94d5-126e8c65a13e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ae959a93-3db7-47d4-94d5-126e8c65a13e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All of the failure instances are in full-zfs-part-1 and full-dne-zfs-part-1 test sessions.&lt;br/&gt;
The same test passed in full-part-1 and full-dne-part-1 test sessions with ldiskfs. 	&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="356460" author="pjones" created="Wed, 14 Dec 2022 18:21:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Jian&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please check to see whether this is indicative of a regression in 2.15.2?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
